et betyr veldig mye for meg men ogs\u00e5 for veldig mange andre, sa S\u00e6tre p\u00e5 pressekonferansen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "b4225638217bf0917d8a4301c1ff4767f2c07cc32c6b42fd3b358a110e84b0f3"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T11:01:54.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Eldar S\u00e6tre ville ikke ha jobben som toppsjef i Statoil. S\u00e5 kom juleferien."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/okonomi/article10611771.ece/ooilh1/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Eldar%20S%C3%A6tre.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/9b20d0dba34e45c0294f56fff09d0cf42dc127b9.jpg?59503ea9"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Ombestemte seg i jula -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "9b20d0dba34e45c0294f56fff09d0cf42dc127b9"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "statoil"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "jobb"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["eldar s\u00e6tre", "helge lund"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/okonomi"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/okonomi/article10611771.ece/ooilh1/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Eldar%20S%C3%A6tre.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Ombestemte seg i jula"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"field": "og-url", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/n